text.section:
To the extent that the Uniform Commercial Code governs a transaction, if one (1) of the following provisions of the Uniform Commercial Code specifies the applicable law, that provision governs and a contrary agreement is effective only to the extent permitted by the law so specified:
KRS 355.2-402;
KRS 355.2A-105 and 355.2A-106;
KRS 355.4-102;
KRS 355.4A-507;
KRS 355.5-116;
KRS 355.8-110;
KRS 355.9-301 to 355.9-307.
